headline: UNP Strong on Dividends & Buybacks Amid Freight Weakness
summary: Union Pacific boosts dividends and buybacks despite freight softness, while its planned Norfolk Southern deal aims to reshape U.S. rail.

headline: CSX Replaces CEO Amid Merger Pressure from Activist Investor
summary: The leadership shakeup comes as the planned Union Pacific-Norfolk Southern merger fuels speculation that CSX may need a partner to stay competitive.
